\c 5
\s Vana vaAdhamu kusvika kuna Nowa
\p
\v 1 Iri ibhuku renhoroondo yedzinza raAdhamu. Pazuva Mwari raakasika munhu nemufananidzo waMwari.
\v 2 Wakavasika murume nemuka­dzi; ndokuvaropafadza, akavatumidza zita rinonzi Munhu, pazuva ravakasikwa.
\v 3 Zvino Adhamu wakararama makore zana nemakumi matatu, akabereka \add mwanakomana\add* wakafanana naye, wakamutodza; akamutumidza zita rinonzi Seti.
\v 4 Zvino mazuva aaAdhamu shure kwekubereka kwake Seti aiva makore mazana masere; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 5 Zvino mazuva ose eupenyu hwaAdhamu aiva makore mazana mapfumba­mwe nemakumi matatu, ndokufa.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Seti wakararama makore zana nemashanu, akabereka Enosi;
\v 7 Seti ndokurarama makore mazana masere nemanomwe shure kwekubereka kwake Enosi, ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 8 Zvino ose mazuva aSeti aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe negumi nema­viri, ndokufa.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Enosi wakararama makore makumi mapfumbamwe, ndokubereka Kenani;
\v 10 Zvino Enosi wakararama shure kwekubereka kwake Kanani makore mazana masere negumi nemashanu; ndokubereka vanako­mana nevanasikana;
\v 11 Zvino mazuva ose aEno­si aiva makore mazana ma­pfumbamwe nemashanu, ndokufa.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Kanani wakararama makore makumi manomwe, akabereka Maharareri;
\v 13 Kanani ndokurarama shure kwekubereka kwake Maharareri makore mazana masere nemakumi mana; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 14 Nemazuva ose aKanani aiva makore mazana mapfumbamwe negumi, ndokufa.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Maharareri wakararama makore makumi matanhatu nemashanu, akabereka Jaredhi.
\v 16 Maharareri ndokuraramama­ shure kwekubereka kwake Jare­dhi makore mazana masere nemakumi matatu, ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 17 Uye mazuva ose aMaharareri aiva makore mazana masere nemakumi mapfumbamwe nemashanu, ndokufa.
\p
\v 18 Zvino Jaredhi wakararama makore zana nemakumi matanhatu nemaviri, akabereka Enoki.
\v 19 Zvino Jaredhi wakararama shure kwekubereka kwake Enoki Jaredhi makore mazana masere; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana;
\v 20 Zvino mazuva ose aJaredhi aiva makore mazana mapfu­mbamwe nemakumi matanhatu nemaviri, ndokufa.
\p
\v 21 Zvino Enoki wakararama makore makumi matanhatu nemashanu, ndokubereka Metu­sera.
\v 22 Zvino Enoki wakafamba naMwari shure kwekubereka kwake Metusera makore mazana matatu; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 23 Nemazuva ose aEnoki aiva makore mazana matatu nema­kumi matanhatu nemashanu.
\v 24 Enoki ndokufamba naMwari, uye haachipo, nekuti Mwari wakamutora.
\p
\v 25 Zvino Metusera wakararama makore zana nemakumi masere namanomwe, ndokubereka Rameki;
\v 26 Zvino Metusera wakararama shure kwekubereka kwake Rameki ma­kore mazana manomwe namakumi masere namaviri; ndokubereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 27 Zvino mazuva ose aMetusera aiva makore mazana mapfu­mbamwe nemakumi matanhatu nemapfu­mbamwe, ndokufa.
\p
\v 28 Rameki ndokurarama makore zana nemakumi masere nemaviri; ndokubereka mwanakomana.
\v 29 Zvino wakamutumidza zita \add kuti\add* Nowa, achiti: Uyu achanyaradza pabasa redu nepakushingaira kwemaoko edu, nekuda kwepasi Jehovha paakapa rushambwa.
\v 30 Rameki akararama shure kwekubereka kwake Nowa, Rameki akagara makore ana mazana mashanu namakumi mapfu­mbamwe namashanu; akabereka vanako­mana navanasikana.
\v 31 Nemazuva ose aRa­meki aiva makore mazana manomwe nemakumi manomwe nema­nomwe, ndokufa.
\p
\v 32 Zvino Nowa waiva nemakore mazana mashanu, Nowa ndokubereka Shemu, naHamu, naJafeti.
